<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>VGC College is committed to protecting the privacy of students, faculty, and staff.</p>
<p>This system stores personal information including names, email addresses, phone numbers, and academic records. All data is used solely for educational administration purposes.</p>
<p>Access to personal data is restricted by role — students can only view their own information, and faculty can only view information for students in their assigned courses.</p>